Text: COI Path and MidwayVincent derateBill NonPrivilegedpst After the Day ahead market ran the COI branch group TTC in the NS direction was changed from MW to MW Path branch group TTC in the NS direction was changed from MW to MW and the MidwayVincent branch group TTC in the NS direction was changed from MW to MW These changes are for HE through HE for operating day The reason for the change is Line outage The first applicable Hour Ahead market to run with these values is HE Cuts will be made in Real Time for HE through HE The ISO will update you of any changes in line rating status Sent by ISO Market Operations The system conditions described in this communication are dynamic and subject to change While the ISO has attempted to reflect the most current accurate information available in preparing this notice system conditions may change suddenly with little or no notice
